questionsAndAnswers.question: What do you need before we get started?
questionsAndAnswers.answer: First and most important, I will need to know as much as possible about you and your business, that way I'll be able to make you a site that truly represents you.

questionsAndAnswers.question: Do you provide Web hosting?
questionsAndAnswers.answer: No, You Have to Provide Hosting, Domain or you can Buy both from some of the best Hosting Provider I know such as Bluehost, hostgator etc.

questionsAndAnswers.question: Do you give us a support after sucessful project completion?
questionsAndAnswers.answer: Yes, On successful project completion of your WordPress or Other Project. I'll give you 15 days of free Technical support.

questionsAndAnswers.question: Do you offer unlimited revisions for free?
questionsAndAnswers.answer: I do provide unlimited revisions for free as per the scope of the project. If you ask for something extra, you will have to pay for it.

questionsAndAnswers.question: Do you do SEO as well?
questionsAndAnswers.answer: Yes, I do provide on page SEO services as well as create a clean and modern wordpress website design

questionsAndAnswers.question: What if I am not satisfied?
questionsAndAnswers.answer: I will keep working on your website until you are 100% satisfied. But still if you are not happy with the work I will refund you.

questionsAndAnswers.question: What if I don't have logo or images?
questionsAndAnswers.answer: I can design an awesome logo for an additional charge and I will find some really good images for free.

questionsAndAnswers.question: Are you available for customized order?
questionsAndAnswers.answer: Yes, I am available for a customized orders and I will provide you a custom quote for that
